==French==
===Etymology===
From an earlier *''falleir'' from Latin [[fallere]]

===Pronunciation===
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /fa.lwaʁ/
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /fa.lwaR/

===Verb===
# To be [[necessary]]
===Conjugation===
''falloir is only used in the [[third person]] [[singular]] ([[il]]) form''

*il [[faut]] (indicative present)
*il [[fallait]] (indicative imperfect)
*il [[fallut]] (past historic)
*il [[faudra]] (future)
*il [[faudrait]] (conditional)
*qu'il [[faille]] (subjunctive present)
*il a [[fallu]] (past participle)
